Bruce French (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bruce_French_(actor) 0 Bruce French (born July 4, 1945) is an American actor who has more than 30 years of acting credits to his name. French was born in Reinbeck, Iowa. He attended the University of Iowa and majored in speech and theatre. He is married to actress/singer Eileen Barnett.
